#. <section class="sutta" id="sn55.32"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn55.32:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.32:0.2"
msgid "4. Puññābhisandavagga"
msgstr "4. Overflowing Merit"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 32. Dutiyapuññābhisandasutta → dutiyābhisandasuttaṃ (bj) | abhisanda 2 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn55.32:0.3"
msgid "32. Dutiyapuññābhisandasutta"
msgstr "32. Overflowing Merit (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.392"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.32:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, puññābhisandā kusalābhisandā sukhassāhārā."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, there are these four kinds of overflowing merit, overflowing "
"goodness that nurture happiness."

msgctxt "sn55.32:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn55.32:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti—"
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the Buddha …"

msgctxt "sn55.32:1.4"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.32:1.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ paṭhamo puññābhisando kusalābhisando sukhassāhāro."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.32:2.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako dhamme … pe …"
msgstr "the teaching …"

msgctxt "sn55.32:2.2"
msgid "saṅghe … pe …."
msgstr "the Saṅgha …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.32:3.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako vigatamalamaccherena cetasā agāraṃ "
"ajjhāvasati muttacāgo payatapāṇi vossaggarato yācayogo dānasaṃvibhāgarato."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, a noble disciple lives at home rid of the stain of stinginess, "
"freely generous, open-handed, loving to let go, committed to charity, loving "
"to give and to share."

msgctxt "sn55.32:3.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ catuttho puññābhisando kusalābhisando sukhassāhāro."
msgstr ""
"This is the fourth kind of overflowing merit, overflowing goodness that "
"nurtures happiness."

msgctxt "sn55.32:3.3"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro puññābhisandā kusalābhisandā sukhassāhārā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These are the four kinds of overflowing merit, overflowing goodness that "
"nurture happiness.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.32:3.4"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
